{"tid":671582,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[行程賜教]東京名古屋大阪遊 八日","createTime":"2018-05-20T09:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T07:16:18.000Z","uid":128301,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"520f6ebfbc63ad0c4cc1256985fc2caef085112d","tid":671582,"uid":128301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"7月去 想知東京去大阪 中間搭多個名古屋o唔ok?<br />\n睇過好似都會順路經過名古屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東京大阪去過幾次 唯獨名古屋未去過<br />\n睇下有冇機會去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay1 晚機9點到東京<br />\nDay2 淺草 鐮倉 江之島 <br />\nDay3 新宿 明治神宮 原宿 東京鐵塔夜景 <br />\n（上面老豆老母未去過，自己就比較想去鐮倉 江之島 湘南海岸）<br />\nDay4 《東京-&gt;名古屋 搭新幹線 1個半鐘到》<br />\n朝早9. 到步 book Airbnb 名古屋城 大須商店街<br />\nDay5 《名古屋-&gt;大阪 搭新幹線 1個半鐘到》<br />\n朝早10. 到步 梅田 道頓掘 心齋橋 黑門市場<br />\nDay6 神戶 Outlet 有馬<br />\nDay7 京都 清水寺 奈良 <br />\nDay8 朝早10點 大阪返香港<br />\n<br />\nHea遊為主 諗緊名古屋係咪可去可不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去一日會唔會太曬氣 同埋冬天可以去埋白川鄉合掌村好似較好？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6079ef7954737d6ed9fbb5d9d860f41d33e62212","tid":671582,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"鎌倉江之島一日都只係勉強夠，仲要加埋淺草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6d3ad2977f6aa04fcd2ec209fe39c8b8a9ca80","tid":671582,"uid":92420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"咁都係hea遊？可能我個節奏慢你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 你晚機去早機返，其實得6日"},{"pid":"25dfcfc644debf845b5664f5d58c65b5e69e65ec","tid":671582,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6d3ad2977f6aa04fcd2ec209fe39c8b8a9ca80","tid":671582,"uid":92420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"咁都係hea遊？可能我個節奏慢你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 你晚機去早機返，其實得6日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"冇錯，實際6日就算東京大阪兩地都趕，仲要加多個名古屋，真係每個地方掂一掂就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n名古屋剩係去個城同大須商店街都幾無謂，尤其是東京大阪大把嘢shopping，大須商店街又唔係有乜特色一定要去"},{"pid":"e609c0d9406db9e823cd1d6a396034845cd3bd24","tid":671582,"uid":133546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"樓主去完？ 想知成個行程chur唔chur？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}